<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/53002071/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The subject will be evaluated in the following way:
PROGRESSIVE EVALUATION
50% Progressive evaluation activities carried out in the classroom, which cannot be recovered and their date may not be programmed beforehand. A minimum of three (3) will be done.
50% Individual project of which:
20% Model in Unisim and Economic assessment spreadsheet
15% Report
15% Final presentation
To pass the progressive evaluation, the following is required:
Given the practical nature of the subject, only three non-justified absences will be allowed.
The minimum grade required in the individual project will be 5/10
EVALUATION ONLY WITH A FINAL EXAM OR EXTRAORDINARY CALL
In case of failing the progressive evaluation, a final exam similar to one or several Case Studies will be carried out. The minimum grade required to pass the exam is 5/10."""@es .

